ji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-19T23:22:50.000Z","msg":"問題佢收錢係你買新機果時收，你掉去邊都走唔到數"},{"pid":"b4c837fc0350b22db50a1d063e216ff48c9adc20","tid":987992,"uid":175598,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-19T23:26:19.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}